      "writtenOn": "2020-09-11T04:44:10Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "AppEngine append max-age:xxx to the Cache-Control header.\nWe will end up having two max-age:xxx if we set it in the header.\n\nIncreased stale-while-revalidate to 28 days.\nI think extending max-age is dangerous, because there\u0027s no way to purge that cache if anything goes wrong.\nhttps://cloud.google.com/appengine/docs/standard/python/how-requests-are-handled#static_cache_expiration",
      "parentUuid": "d6b15122_c73939e9",
      "revId": "afd49a5a824026fd48100e2014389d607b32a980",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
